      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously preserved. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, glass-like finish, free of any chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, still smelling like new with no signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been garage-kept and maintained to the highest possible standards; this is a rare find for a discerning buyer looking for a 'like-new' experience.",
