    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who isn't concerned with perfection. The engine starts up every time and the car drives fine, though you may notice some minor cosmetic wear on the interior and exterior, such as small scratches and upholstery fading. It has been maintained reasonably well, but it will likely need some routine suspension work or new tires in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, functional car that gets the job done without the high price tag of a mint-condition model.",
