    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a well-maintained 2019 Audi Q7 Prestige in Moonlight Blue Metallic. This vehicle offers a perfect balance of luxury and utility for the discerning driver. The exterior retains a high gloss finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professionally touched-up scuff on the lower rear bumper consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the Pistachio Beige leather interior is clean and inviting; the driver\u2019s seat shows slight, natural creasing on the outer bolster, but the cabin remains strictly non-smoking and free of any tears or stains. Mechanically, this Q7 is robust and road-ready. It features a comprehensive service history with a recent oil service and brake pad replacement performed just 2,000 miles ago. All sophisticated electronics, including the Audi Virtual Cockpit, panoramic sunroof, and the 19-speaker Bose Surround Sound system, function perfectly. The all-season tires have approximately 70% tread remaining. This is a reliable, premium family hauler that has been treated with respect and is ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
